{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the girls camps were maybe in some field 5 or 10 blocks away, 10-- 5 or 10 fields away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They kept boys and girls different, teenagers, which was probably not a bad idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- particularly for the parents of religious girls, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so that was that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my activities when I-- when I came to-- to London, in High Wycombe already, while I was there in the year, I went to apprentice classes to the High Wycombe school, in High Wycombe, to apprentice classes for cabinetmaking.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I used-- after work was down the street, a few blocks down the street, I'd go from the factory to apprentice classes for a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then also-- a couple of times a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then also couple times a week I went to a youth club, still in High Wycombe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got into that habit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did boxing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We played ping-pong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Got into boxing there, and ping-pong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On Sundays, we took bicycle rides to the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was the only Jewish-- there was another Jewish boy there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they used to call me Jew boy, but it was friendly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not-- it was not-- you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and there was another Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But did not refer to him as Jew boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They did not refer to him as such.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I guess he didn't-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- but it was friendly and it was pleasant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got into London, we had started a certain system of doing things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to classes, took classes in the evening, classes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What sort of classes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For-- I think it was in relation to-- to either-- either cabinet-- it was not cabinet, specifically.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
